### ServiceNow Knowledge Base API Test File
### Use this with the REST Client extension in VS Code

### Start the server first:
### node quick-start.js

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Search for password-related articles
GET http://localhost:3000/api/knowledge/search?q=password

### Search for VPN troubleshooting
GET http://localhost:3000/api/knowledge/search?q=vpn

### Search with category filter
GET http://localhost:3000/api/knowledge/search?q=email&category=Email

### Get specific article
GET http://localhost:3000/api/knowledge/article/1

### Get popular articles
GET http://localhost:3000/api/knowledge/popular

### Get all categories
GET http://localhost:3000/api/knowledge/categories

### Analyze technical issue
POST http://localhost:3000/api/knowledge/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue_description": "User cannot connect to VPN",
  "error_message": "Error 800: Unable to establish connection",
  "system_info": {
    "os": "Windows 10",
    "software": "Cisco AnyConnect",
    "version": "4.9.0"
  }
}

### Another analysis example
POST http://localhost:3000/api/knowledge/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue_description": "User forgot password and needs to reset it",
  "error_message": "Access denied when trying to login"
}

### API Documentation
GET http://localhost:3000/api/docs 